sentences: Mister Lies is a musical project started in 2012 by American electronic musician, record producer and multimedia artist Nick Zanca.
His debut release, the Hidden Neighbors EP, was self-released anonymously on his Bandcamp account in February 2012.
His first full-length album, Mowgli, was released by Lefse Records in February 2013.
In May 2014, Zanca announced via his Twitter that Brooklyn-based label Orchid Tapes would release his second album, Shadow, later in the year.
Mass EP (2012), collaboration with Different Sleep [self-released]

His music is a blend of ambient pop and EDM and has been compared to "1990s trip-hop" by Pitchfork Media, who called his music a "steadily building velvet sound, the kind that you want to wrap yourself in."
In May 2014, Zanca announced via his Twitter that Brooklyn-based label Orchid Tapes would release his second album, Shadow, later in the year.
